  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Model Risk Level 5. Thirteen credibility factors evaluated; seven assessed with achieved levels below required, six flagged as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo UQ performed. Decision: Accepted under Minimal profile. NOTE: hasContextOfUse is intentionally absent — intended-use scope is undefined (W-ON-01 trigger).",
