      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented regression test suite and traceable build records required at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Solver version control confirmed; however, regression test coverage covers only 40% of relevant flow regimes and build records lack traceability to certified compiler chain. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
