      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive law selection justified with sensitivity analysis against alternative model forms.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected without comparison to LES or RSM alternatives. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen) used without evaluation of Arora or Faghih-Sharp models. Flagged as epistemic gap; factor not assessed."
    },
