      "acceptanceCriteria": "Uncertainty distributions assigned to all material and boundary input parameters; Monte Carlo propagation with convergence demonstrated.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ initiated but only three of eleven input parameters assigned distributions; blood viscosity and hemolysis model coefficients treated as fixed. Convergence of Monte Carlo not demonstrated. Flagged as epistemic gap; factor not assessed."
    },
