    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile, the credibility evidence package is accepted as structurally complete. Thirteen factors have been scaffolded; seven carry assessed levels and six are flagged as epistemic gaps at MRL 5. The package is forwarded for regulatory review with the understanding that all seven assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels and six factors remain unassessed. No context of use has been formally recorded in this package.",
